fields.name: CodeGram
fields.description:
# CodeGram

A comprehensive social platform where developers share code snippets, discover solutions, and build meaningful connections.

## Features

- Code snippet sharing with syntax highlighting
- Community voting and discussions
- Developer profile portfolios
- Real-time collaboration features
- Advanced search and filtering

fields.name: ToolForge
fields.description:
# ToolForge

An intelligent command-line tool builder that helps developers create custom CLI tools with AI assistance.

## Features

- AI-powered code generation
- Custom CLI tool templates
- Git and package manager integration
- Workflow automation scripts
- Cross-platform compatibility

fields.name: Sarah Chen
fields.title: Senior Developer
fields.content: CodeGram has completely changed how I share and discover code snippets. The community is incredibly supportive and the platform is beautifully designed.

fields.name: Marcus Rodriguez
fields.title: Full-Stack Developer
fields.content: Appnity builds exactly what developers need. Their attention to detail and understanding of developer workflows is unmatched.
